name: Hard Starts #1
description:
Another threshold focused session that adds an element of race specificity to it. The main set of intervals consists of 7min descending threshold efforts preceded by a high-intensity 30sec effort. 



This session closely reflects the demands you will face in a criterium race, with a challenging start or surge at the beginning of a long, sustained effort.
            


            This workout is also available as Video workout by a MyWhoosh coach Si Bradeley
